will be the official thread for voicing your ideas and concerns with the recent &quot;nerfing&quot; of the Luclin zone The Grey. Keep the discussion civil, and the ranting to a minimum. I will be notifying other boards of this thread, and with any luck we can submit this to Verant to change the zone back to it's previous state.<br>
<br>
The facts, taken from Castersrealm:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> The Grey zone in Luclin was patched live a short while ago.<br>
