/eye Verant.... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/udamoens.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Damoen S</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/11/01 6:18:47 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Petition for Verant, RE: The Grey</span><hr size=1> I would like to see a reason why they changed the zone.  I am not saying that the zone didn't need the change.  I would like to know why it happened.<br>
